Some ND indexing on 1d Arrays -----
 array (1 2 3 4 5)
 index (1) -> 2
 index (0) -> 1
 index (-1) -> 0
 index (4) -> 5
 index (5) -> 0
 index (6) -> 0
Some ND indexing on 2D Arrays -----
 array ((11 12 13 14 15) (21 22 23 24 25))
 index (0 0) -> 11
 index (1 1) -> 22
 index (1 0) -> 12
 index (0 1) -> 21
 index (10 10) -> 0
 index (3 1) -> 24
 index (1 3) -> 0
 index (0 2) -> 0
 index (0 1) -> 21
Some ND indexing on 3D Arrays -----
 array (((111 112 113 114 115) (21 22 23 24 25)) ((211 212 213 214 215) (221 222 223 224 225)))
 index (1 1 1) -> 222
 index (1 0 1) -> 212
 index (1 0 0) -> 112
 index (1) -> 112
 index () -> 111
 index (1 1 1 1) -> 0
Some ND indexing on 1d Arrays with non default defaults -----
 array (1 2 3 4 5)
 index (-1) -> 505
 index (*) -> 1
 index (0) -> 1
 index (1) -> 2
 index (4) -> 5
 index (5) -> 505
